metadata.name: Etamin
metadata.description:
Etamin lives on the central planet of the Draco constellation.

She has a special reaction team under her command. They protect the planet from the enemy. 

Her dragon is the most powerful in the entire galaxy. It has the power of a stupefying mist - the dragon creates a mist that contains particles of a potent substance. 

There is only one escape from this smoke - running, and very quickly.
